    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think in this case it's a misuse of `require`. I think you should be using `revert` in this case: https://docs.soliditylang.org/en/latest/control-structures.html#revert-statement\r\n\r\nRequire is for checking preconditions based on some inputs. In this case all you need is an unconditional revert.",
